  "name": "SpaceKonceptRental - KB Ingestion to Pinecone",
  "active": false,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# DRIVE TRIGGERS\n\n- Watches approved KB files created or updated in Google Drive.\n- Tags each run as `created` or `updated` before downloading the file.\n- Removes duplicate file events inside the same trigger batch so new files still continue.\n- Sends changed files into the ingestion path.\n\n## Required manual configuration:\n\n- **KB File Created**\n  - `folderToWatch.value`: Set this to the Google Drive folder that stores approved KB files.\n- **KB File Updated**\n  - `folderToWatch.value`: Set this to the same Google Drive folder that stores approved KB files.",
        "height": 652,
        "width": 980,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000901",
      "name": "Drive triggers group",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1328,
        -256
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# CHUNK PREPARATION\n\n- Adds source metadata from the Google Drive file.\n- Loads and splits document content for retrieval.",
        "height": 652,
